{"tid":1855844,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"突然間覺得自己人生好廢","createTime":"2020-02-01T09:47:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-01T17:02:00.000Z","uid":323832,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"63c6db647e7c3439d934d7ff4002139d6a4455f2","tid":1855844,"uid":323832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T09:47:12.000Z","msg":"自問做野好唔細心，好難改~<br />\n<br />\n今年年頭已經有人同我講，<br />\n<br />\n老細好大機會叫我做到完約就離開（7~8月左右），<br />\n<br />\n我諗到甘已經好灰，我實俾人炒硬！<br />\n<br />\n呢件事我唔敢同其他人講，包括父母+朋友。<br />\n<br />\n我想轉工，但E家市道甘差，好難搵工，<br />\n<br />\n就算俾你搵到，都仲要睇下配唔配合返夜校+實習既時間。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所有野都好煩~<br />\n<br />\n而且我夜晚仲要返夜校，而個degree係要讀兩年，兼要係機構實習！<br />\n<br />\n我真係覺得自己好廢，無曬人生動力。<br />\n<br />\n讀完書都仲係甘廢，都仲係甘唔細心，連譚仔姐姐都好過我。"},{"pid":"930287bfedf47225953702d689b7fc8639984d26","tid":1855844,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T09:49:42.000Z","msg":"Die die die"},{"pid":"3697ef9ff3d679e5e22a05348318a3c520c7ce1a","tid":1855844,"uid":121063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T09:49:46.000Z","msg":"巴打加油 會唔會係份工唔適合你 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c07e9e4e96cc85cb25a816237958639071cc191a","tid":1855844,"uid":53278,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T09:50:29.000Z","msg":"梗係啦<br />\n你連個咁字都要打做甘<br />\n唔炒你炒邊個"},{"pid":"5ed10ae11986fb222bc46f38347d90fba20caaba","tid":1855844,"uid":60434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T09:51:19.000Z","msg":"個市咁樣出面唔會請p牌仔"},{"pid":"d245f2138b9586f806ca89c0e35c5561a69f2b92","tid":1855844,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T09:51:43.000Z","msg":"垃圾, 你咁做份份都比人炒架啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d8927200c3b20eed55e47dc5ebef14b67c995ce","tid":1855844,"uid":252091,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0